<div class="row">
	<div class="span12 landing_hero_info rounded-corners shadow">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="span5">
				<h2>we bring the MBA case study experience online. for free.</h2>
				<h2>develop the network and the mind of an MBA withouth paying a dime. </h2>
			</div>
